OL,3,CHome Office urged to investigate new
OL,4,CGreen MSP in UK on student visa
OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatives are calling
OL,7,Fon the Home Office to investigate a
OL,8,Fnewly elected Green MSP accused of
OL,9,Fbreaking immigration rules.
OL,11,FQ Manivannan was elected to the
OL,12,FScottish Parliament last week after
OL,13,Fwinning a seat on the Edinburgh and
OL,14,FLothians East regional list.
OL,16,FManivannan, who has described
OL,17,Fthemselves as a "queer Tamil
OL,18,Fimmigrant", is non-binary and uses
OL,19,Fthey/them pronouns, is currently
OL,20,Fliving in Scotland on a student visa.
OL,26,@yD@QOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
