OL,3,CHome Office urged to investigate new
OL,4,CGreen MSP in UK on student visa
OL,6,FOn Friday, Manivannan said they would
OL,7,Fapply for a graduate visa to work in
OL,8,Fthe UK for a longer period, as well as
OL,9,Fa Global Talent visa to remain for the
OL,10,Fduration of their parliamentary career.
OL,12,FRecent eligibility changes to become
OL,13,Fan MSP meant Manivannan could stand in
OL,14,Fthe election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
