OL,3,CHome Office urged to investigate new
OL,4,CGreen MSP in UK on student visa
OL,6,FBut the Scottish Conservatives have
OL,7,Faccused the new MSP of breaching the
OL,8,Fterms of their visa, saying the
OL,9,Fguidance was "clear that holders of
OL,10,Fstudent visas are only permitted to
OL,11,Fwork for a maximum of 20 hours per
OL,12,Fweek, whether voluntary or paid".
OL,14,FOne of the party's 12 MSPs, Stephen
OL,15,FKerr, has written to Home Secretary
OL,16,FShabana Mahmood, urging her to
OL,17,Finvestigate the alleged breach of
OL,18,Frules.
OL,26,@qD@NOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778659579
OL,3,CHome Office urged to investigate new
OL,4,CGreen MSP in UK on student visa
OL,6,F"I'm calling on the Home Office to
OL,7,Flook into this case, because I can't
OL,8,Fsee how Q Manivannan can fulfil the
OL,9,Fduties of an MSP without breaching the
OL,10,Fstrict terms under which a student
OL,11,Fvisa is issued," he said.
OL,13,F"Being an MSP is a demanding, full-
OL,14,Ftime job that can't possibly be
OL,15,Fcarried out effectively by working
OL,16,Fless than 20 hours per week."
OL,18,FHe added that he was "almost certain"
OL,19,FManivannan had already breached the
OL,20,Fworking limit during the course of the
OL,21,Felection campaign.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@]O]zD@VOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
