CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778659579
OL,3,CHome Office urged to investigate new
OL,4,CGreen MSP in UK on student visa
OL,6,FKerr said immigration rules "must be
OL,7,Fapplied fairly and equally to all",
OL,8,Fadding that "they certainly can't be
OL,9,Fbreached by a lawmaking MSP".
OL,11,F"This is a shambles entirely of the
OL,12,FScottish Greens' making - and they owe
OL,13,Fan explanation to voters in
OL,14,FEdinburgh," he continued.
OL,16,F"If they had done any due diligence or
OL,17,Fcandidate vetting, they would have
OL,18,Frealised the pitfalls of this
OL,19,Fcandidate standing."
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@bO]pD@MOUqD@\O]sD@AOUvD@KO]xD@
