OL,3,CHome Office urged to investigate new
OL,4,CGreen MSP in UK on student visa
OL,6,FManivannan said in a statement on
OL,7,FMonday evening that every MSP at
OL,8,FHolyrood unanimously voted to allow
OL,9,Feveryone with the right to live in the
OL,10,FUK to stand in elections, "including
OL,11,Fnew Scots on visas like me".
OL,13,F"I am a Commonwealth citizen and am
OL,14,Fcurrently on a student visa which will
OL,15,Fexpire later this year. Having passed
OL,16,Fmy grant-funded PhD and viva, I am
OL,17,Fable to work full-time," he said.
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@[O]
